flowchart TD
    A[User Interaction]:::box --> B[Content Selection]:::box
    B --> C[Request Content from Server]:::box
    C --> D[Authenticate User]:::box
    D -->|Success| E[Fetch Content Metadata]:::box
    D -->|Failure| F[Show Error Message]:::box
    F --> A
    E --> G[Retrieve Content from CDN]:::box
    G --> H[Buffering Content]:::box
    H --> I[Start Playback]:::box
    I --> J[User Interaction (Controls)]:::box
    J -->|Play/Pause| I
    J -->|Seek| K[Update Playback Position]:::box
    K --> I
    J -->|Stop| L[Close Streaming Session]:::box
    L --> A

    classDef box fill:#87CEEB,stroke:#FF4500,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef background fill:#F5F5DC;
    class A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,I,J,K,L background;